- Finding 转换规则: ~/.claude/rules-t3/review-templates.md <!-- anchor: finding-transition -->

For each finding use structured format: ID, Severity, Category, Type (defect_fix/behavior_change), Before-behavior, After-behavior, Evidence (file:line), Impact, Repair hypothesis (optional, non-authoritative).
Repair hypothesis is advisory only and has no execution authority.
If the finding touches invariants, risk_modules, or red-flag patterns
