**Phase 0**

Contract Pack 不是空的，`INV-001/003/004/005` 和 `CE-001/002/003` 都有对应测试或 mitigation；我也跑了 batch1 相关后端测试，当前是 `87 passed`。但 `INV-002` 的 verification 映射不准确，属于 process finding：计划把 “`da_knowledge_point_map` 不变” 映射到 `test_get_mastery_excludes_big_concepts`，这并没有验证映射表本身。[plan.md:844](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L844) [test_service.py:239](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py#L239)

**Findings**

1. `F001` Severity: Critical; Category: `code-bug`; Type: `defect_fix`. Before-behavior: `python scripts/migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py --dry-run` 应只预演，不落库。 After-behavior: 迁移各步骤先 `commit()`，最后的 `rollback()` 已无法回滚，`--dry-run` 仍会建表、改 `L0 -> evidence`、写 aliases/evidence_ids。 Evidence: [migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py:105](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/scripts/migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py#L105) [migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py:165](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/scripts/migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py#L165) [migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py:171](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/scripts/migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py#L171) [migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py:183](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/scripts/migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py#L183) [migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py:210](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/scripts/migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py#L210) [plan.md:49](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L49). 本地最小复现里，执行 dry-run 后仍得到 `big_concepts_exists=1`、`l0_after=evidence`。 Impact: 运维按计划用 dry-run 验库时，会对真实 `knowledge.db` 做不可预期写入。 Repair hypothesis: likely repair direction 是把整次迁移放进单事务并取消中途提交；forbidden fix patterns to avoid 是“保留中途 commit，只在末尾补 rollback”或“仅跳过部分步骤”；requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate.

2. `F002` Severity: High; Category: `code-bug`; Type: `defect_fix`. Before-behavior: 相同 `big_concept` 文本出现在不同 module 时，应按 module 生成不同 BigConcept，并把概念映射回各自模块。[plan.md:81](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L81) After-behavior: 代码把 `text_to_id` 键设成纯文本，后写入的模块会覆盖先前模块；随后 `_build_concept_map()` 又只通过文本回查，导致跨模块概念被绑到最后一个模块的 BC。 Evidence: [migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py:103](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/scripts/migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py#L103) [migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py:114](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/scripts/migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py#L114) [migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py:118](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/scripts/migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py#L118) [migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py:156](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/scripts/migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py#L156). 本地复现里，M1 和 M2 的两个概念最终都映射到了 M2 的 BigConcept。 Impact: navigation/big_concept_id 会稳定性错误，属于真实数据上的错误分组。 Repair hypothesis: likely repair direction 是改成 module-scoped identity，而不是 text-only 查表；forbidden fix patterns to avoid 是“last-write-wins by label text”或“靠自然排序赌不冲突”；requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate.

3. `F003` Severity: High; Category: `code-bug`; Type: `defect_fix`. Before-behavior: `set_review_status` 的审核人应来自当前已认证用户，且 `user_id` 缺失应拒绝，这也是计划写明的边界。[plan.md:488](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L488) [plan.md:491](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L491) After-behavior: 路由层直接 `model_dump()` 原样透传，服务层无条件信任 `op_data["user_id"]`；`user_id` 缺失时状态仍会推进，只是 `reviewed_by=None`。 Evidence: [router.py:72](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py#L72) [router.py:79](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py#L79) [service.py:292](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py#L292) [service.py:299](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py#L299) [test_edit_extended.py:104](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_edit_extended.py#L104). 我用最小脚本直接复现到 `applied=1, reviewed_by=None`。 Impact: 审核链路可被伪造或产生无审计记录的“已审核”状态，审核追溯失真。 Repair hypothesis: likely repair direction 是把 reviewer identity 绑定到认证上下文并把请求体里的 reviewer 标识视为不可信；forbidden fix patterns to avoid 是“继续信任前端传 user_id”或“缺失时默默写 None”；requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate.

4. `F004` Severity: High; Category: `code-bug`; Type: `defect_fix`. Before-behavior: `reorder` 应改变 BigConcept 下概念的返回顺序，并按计划回写到 source-of-truth。[plan.md:500](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L500) [plan.md:580](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L580) After-behavior: `apply_edits()` 只改 PG 的 `display_order`，`get_graph()` 组 `concept_ids` 时完全不读 `display_order`，仍按 map 查询顺序返回；同时 backwrite 没有 `reorder` 分支，而 knowledge.db 迁移也没给 concept 加 `display_order` 列。 Evidence: [service.py:44](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py#L44) [service.py:56](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py#L56) [service.py:84](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py#L84) [service.py:303](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py#L303) [service.py:382](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/service.py#L382) [migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py:71](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/scripts/migrate_knowledge_hierarchy.py#L71) [test_edit_extended.py:203](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_edit_extended.py#L203) [review-handoff-batch1.md:56](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-review-handoff-batch1.md#L56). 本地复现里，`display_order` 已变成 `C=0/A=1/B=2`，但 `get_graph()` 的 `concept_ids` 仍是 `['A','B','C']`。 Impact: Task 6 的 reorder 功能对 API/前端无可见效果，而且重同步后不可持久。 Repair hypothesis: likely repair direction 是让排序语义在读路径和权威存储里闭环；forbidden fix patterns to avoid 是“继续依赖数据库自然顺序”或“只改 PG 临时投影不改权威源”；requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate.

5. `F005` Severity: Medium; Category: `test-gap`; Type: `defect_fix`. Before-behavior: `INV-002` 需要测试直接证明 `da_knowledge_point_map` 在本批改动前后不变。 After-behavior: 计划把它映射到 `test_get_mastery_excludes_big_concepts`，而这个测试只检查 mastery 结果里没有 BigConcept ID，从头到尾没比对 `DaKnowledgePointMap` 的行数或内容。 Evidence: [plan.md:22](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L22) [plan.md:844](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L844) [test_service.py:239](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_service.py#L239). Impact: Contract Pack 对一条核心连续性不变量给出了错误的“已验证”信号。 Repair hypothesis: likely repair direction 是把 verification 改成显式快照/比对 DA 映射表；forbidden fix patterns to avoid 是“继续拿 mastery 结果当代理证明”；requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate.

**Phase 1-3 补充**

测试并非完全无效，所以我继续做了实现审查；但覆盖薄弱点很集中。`test_migration.py` 从未走过 `dry_run` 分支，[test_migration.py:154](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_migration.py#L154)；`TestSetReviewStatus` 只测 service 层且总是手工传 `user_id`，[test_edit_extended.py:104](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_edit_extended.py#L104)；`TestReorder` 只断言列值变化，不断言 `get_graph()` 的用户可见顺序，[test_edit_extended.py:203](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_edit_extended.py#L203)。另外还有一个未单列为 finding 的残余风险：当前没有覆盖“PG 已有旧版投影数据时的升级/重同步”路径，发布前最好做一次真实迁移演练。

结论：**FAIL**。
